            <div class="container">
                
                <h2 align="left">What is Cinemango?</h2>
                <p> Cinemango is a platform for people to discover movies currently playing in their neighborhoods<br>
                Cinemango can also be used to gather general information about movies and theaters</p>
                
                <h2 align="left">Where can I purchase gift cards?</h2>
                <p> Gift cards are currently sold at Target, Walmart and other major retailers.  <br>
                Alternatively, you can purchase a gift card online!</p>
                
                <h2 align="left">Why do you display ads?</h2>
                <p> We display advertisements to generate revenue!  <br>
                You can disable advertisements by downloading adblock.</p>
                
                <h2 align="left">How do I find a theatre?</h2>
                <p> Type in your zipcode or city/state in the searchbar! <br>
                Alternatively, share your location with us and we can find the nearest theatres to you. </p>
                
                <h2 align="left">How do I find a movie?</h2>
                <p> Search for it in the search bar <br>
                Alternatively, select a movie from a theatre. </p>
          
            
            <h2 align="left">How do I purchase a ticket?</h2>
                <p> Go to the theatre page and select a showtime. <br>
                    Fill out the forms to proceed purchasing a ticket. <br>
                You can purchase with a credit card or gift card.</p>
